| Funci√≥                       | LVM (Linux) | Storage Spaces (Windows) |
|-----------------------------|-------------|----------------------------|
| Snapshots                  | ‚úî S√≠        | ‚úñ No                       |
| Mirroring                  | ‚úî S√≠        | ‚úî S√≠                       |
